{"type": "article", "id": 22449, "title": "可组合的咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-18T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113116RlH9TDWYhmJNB28i.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞典设计师 Markus Johansson 带来的一组咖啡桌，在方形桌面旁连接了一块略高的圆形桌面，都是橡木做的。它真正的用途在于不同颜色和型号的咖啡桌可以拼在一起，利用错位的高度让他们形成一个新的拼桌，可以适应不同的需求，也让空间显得有趣。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113114w3ATQabOn2yE94UL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.85207824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113114YFKQIszxu46hpgNb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113115GwhK6gMUilz5mSIc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80684597\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071131150dzCqYvfcREnt4Sm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113115dKMIZRBxmf1nXhaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}